data.description: Welcome to 606 Cypress Drive, Mount Airy a A Modern Gem Nestled on Nearly 2 Acres of Serene Landscape Discover the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and tranquility in this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, meticulously crafted in 2021/2022. Situated on a sprawling 1.93-acre lot, this residence promises an unparalleled living experience in Mount Airy's most sought-after neighborhood. Elegant Living Reimagined Step inside to find a haven of elegance and warmth, where every detail has been carefully considered for your utmost comfort. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting space for gatherings of all sizes. High-end stainless steel appliances, and sumptuous granite countertops are ready to inspire your culinary adventures. A Master Retreat Designed for Serenity The spacious master bedroom is a masterpiece of design, offering additional insulation for a quieter, more climate-controlled environment, ensuring restful nights and peaceful mornings. The en-suite master bath is a sanctuary of its own, featuring double vanities and ample space for a spa-like experience every day. Outdoor Living at Its Finest Step outside to the impressive 20x24 rear back patio, where the beauty of Mount Airy unfolds before your eyes. This outdoor oasis is perfect for entertaining, relaxing, or simply enjoying the breathtaking surroundings. The property's vast acreage offers privacy and plenty of room for exploration and activities, complemented by an outdoor shop for your hobbies or storage needs. Luxury and Convenience in Harmony With its 2021/2022 construction, this home offers the peace of mind of modern living, complete with all the conveniences you desire. Ample parking ensures that you and your guests always have space, while the extensive outdoor area invites endless possibilities for enjoyment. A Location Like No Other 606 Cypress Drive, this home is more than an address a it's a gateway to the lifestyle you've been dreaming of. With nearly 2 acres of land, the tranquility of nature is at your doorstep, yet you're never far from the amenities and attractions that make Mount Airy so convenient. Don't miss the opportunity to make 606 Cypress Drive your own. Experience the perfect combination of modern luxury and natural beauty, all in one exceptional home.
